Decentralized AI Dataset Labeling L1
Overview

Decentralized AI Dataset Labeling L1 provides a scalable infrastructure for crowdsourcing, validating, and rewarding dataset labeling activities for AI training.

Features
Decentralized labeling marketplace
Contributor reputation tracking
Quality validation mechanisms
Incentivized participation
Transparent dataset contributions
Architecture
Labeling Registry

Stores labeled data and contributor metadata.

Validation Engine

Ensures accuracy through consensus or redundancy.

Reward Module

Distributes incentives to contributors.

Reputation System

Tracks labeling quality and contributor trust.

Use Cases
AI training dataset labeling
Computer vision annotation
NLP dataset creation
Crowdsourced data enrichment
